Types of Deployment
-------------------

| Type                  | Description                         | Example            |
| --------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ------------------ |
| Local Deployment      | Runs only on your computer          | Jupyter Notebook   |
| On-Premise Deployment | Runs inside a company's own servers | Bank servers       |
| Cloud Deployment      | Runs on cloud servers               | Hugging Face, AWS  |
| Mobile Deployment     | Runs inside Android/iPhone apps     | Food delivery app  |
| Desktop Deployment    | Installed on Windows/Mac            | Microsoft Word     |
| Edge Deployment       | Runs directly on devices            | Security camera AI |
| Embedded Deployment   | Runs inside hardware                | Smart TV           |

