=========

Deployment is the process of taking software or an AI model from your development environment and making it available on a server so real users can access and use it reliably through a website, mobile app, desktop application, or API.

For an AI engineer, deployment is the final step that transforms a trained model into a real-world product that customers, businesses, and applications can use.









